# Redesign of Contacts Analysis Section

Redesign the "Contacts and Departments" section to be more functional, visually unique, and data-rich.

## Proposed Changes

### [AbmStrategy.tsx](file:///Users/user/Documents/Command%20Center%20Cockpit/Canopi_Antigravity/canopi---intel-excels/src/pages/AbmStrategy.tsx)

#### [MODIFY] [AbmStrategy.tsx](file:///Users/user/Documents/Command%20Center%20Cockpit/Canopi_Antigravity/canopi---intel-excels/src/pages/AbmStrategy.tsx)
- Add "Potencial Geral de Contato" (`pot_geral`) to `matrixViews`.
- Implement specific [getMatrixScore](file:///Users/user/Documents/Command%20Center%20Cockpit/Canopi_Antigravity/canopi---intel-excels/src/pages/AbmStrategy.tsx#2115-2150) logic for `pot_geral`.
- Define unique, illustrated, and functional `actionCards` for:
    - `recept` (Receptividade)
    - `access` (Acessibilidade)
    - `pos` (Posicionamento)
    - `pot` (Oportunidade / Budget)
    - `pot_geral` (Potencial Geral de Contato)
- Ensure each heatmap has its own set of 3 cards (2 small + 1 large/wide).
- Replace generic "Fit Firmográfico" and "Fit Tecnográfico" sections with the new heatmaps or just remove them as they are legacy.

#### [DELETE] Legacy Sections
- Remove the "Fit Firmográfico" and "Fit Tecnográfico" cards at the bottom of the page.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1.  Open `http://localhost:3000` in the browser.
2.  Navigate to the ABM Strategy page.
3.  Scroll down to "Análise de Contatos e Departamentos".
4.  Verify that there are 5 distinct heatmaps (Posicionamento, Potencial Vertical, Receptividade, Acessibilidade, Potencial Geral).
5.  Check that each heatmap has unique action cards on the right.
6.  Click on buttons in the action cards to verify they trigger the correct modals (or at least don't crash).
7.  Verify that "Fit Firmográfico" and "Fit Tecnográfico" sections are gone.
